# How To Play
 This project is called Dirty Soccer. The game concept is very simple: Players will try to score as many goals as possible before the time runs out. 
 In this single player demo, players will get a chance to free roam to get players used to the game mechanics and scoring. Players will be able to see
 the first map and depending on which version youre looking at, you will be able to play solo, with AI, or multiplayer to see whose the best Dirty Soccer
 Player
 
 #User Guide
- How to install demo version:
  -Github
    - APK file of the game will be uploaded to Github repository. User can go to Github repository through internet application such as Chrome
    to reach the repository and manually download the APK file to install and play.
